Update an existing user's profile information.

Updates the specified user with the provided information.
Only the fields included in the input will be updated.
Requires authentication as the user being updated or as an admin.

Example:
```graphql
mutation {
  updateUser(
    id: "123",
    input: {
      firstName: "Updated",
      lastName: "Name",
      phone: "9876543210"
    }
  ) {
    id
    firstName
    lastName
    email
    phone
  }
}
```

Update wallet settings.

Updates the status or limits of a wallet.

Example:
```graphql
mutation {
  updateWallet(id: "abc123", input: { status: "active", dailyLimit: 2000 }) {
    id
    status
    dailyLimit
  }
}
```

